Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocademy Visual Effects Awards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...for Space Titanic...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:27.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonsoir, madames et messieurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell?! I mean, is that Morita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:36.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:36.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:42.82,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:42.82,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:57.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:57.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:03.74,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:03.74,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:09.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:09.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:14.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:14.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.19,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.19,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:26.53,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:26.53,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:31.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:31.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:37.54,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:37.54,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:41.28,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:41.28,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What is that man doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on T-TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Mocademy Awards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollywood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Visual Effects Award? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:14.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means that Morita-san did the CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:16.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's blonde!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:20.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! What's going on? What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:19.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:20.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:24.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it. We haven't seen him in a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be quiet! You're causing trouble for the other patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:28.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we finally see him again - on TV!\NAnd it's the Mocademy Awards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I'm sorry. Everyone, quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:29.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's blonde...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocademy Visual Effects Award!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone, be quiet, his speech is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:37.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, wow, what should I talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got put up to this at such short notice,\Nand I'm not good with speeches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, since I'm bad at this, I'll say simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:51.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, a message to the man who, in the middle of everything,\Ndumped it all on me, from the character designs and CG action...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:57.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To background effects and the motion capture models,\Nsaying to me, "I'll leave everything to your talents."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when poor little me tried to go back to Japan saying,\N"This wasn't in my contract, so I'm leaving"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...placed me on house arrest for a year\Nin a studio in the deserts of Arizona...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, saying, "We're not going\Nto make it in time for the premiere,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:11.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...made me do not only the CGs but also\Nmatte paintings for backgrounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:15.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually telling me so amiably, "Actually,\Nwe need them by tomorrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:18.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell is "As feeling!" supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:23.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I bitterly (yet honestly) complained that,\N"I can't draw anything without model sheets,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...he handed me this chunky screenplay with a broad smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:31.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this was the {\i1}screenplay.{\i0} What\NI wanted was the model sheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the latter part of it was blank...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then in the end, he starts asking me\Nonce again in a friendly fashion:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:41.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, Shinobu, what do you think will happen for the ending?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was like, "Whatever," and answered, "I'm\Nsleepy," and he goes ahead and uses it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if he's going that far, isn't it like\Nhalf the screenplay was done by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't simple at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:51.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say, "Fork over my half of\Nyour damned box office revenue!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:56.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but the man then hurried off on a vacation, saying\N"I'll leave the rest to you," and is actually absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To the director, Peter Lucas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:05.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morita-san... why do you always do whatever\Nyou feel like doing, no matter where you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:05.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! I still have other things I need to say to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:09.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I will dedicate every last bit of my 400 million fee to\Nhiring a lawyer and I will come back to this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see you will be in court!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pry away at least five times the attorney fee from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs39}I'll be back—!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:22.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone I know on TV before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-san, please be quiet in the hospital room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! I mean, would you normally act that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's blonde!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he was never normal to begin with, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,America?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When is he coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe in half a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want him to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's good to keep trying until you've\Ntried everything you've wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:06.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she will do once Morita-san comes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:27.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make it to heaven before I knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:31.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The familiar faces of my classmates\Nare all there like a kaleidoscope...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-M-M-Morita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he has a light concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please head over to outpatient care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:50.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, we're leaving now. H-Hagu, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh... e-everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Today's Morning Plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}First, let's start with this astonishing news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\an4\shad0\bord0.1\be1\c&HEAEDEC&\3c&HEAEDEC&\fs27\frz5.233\frx352\fry352\pos(562,416)}Receives the\NMocademy Award
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\3c&H745D51&\c&HE7ECEB&\an4\shad0\be1\fs28\fsp-0.5\frx2\fry348\frz5.674\pos(650,324)}A Japanese\NDelightfully\NWins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:12.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A mysterious Japanese man received\Nthe Mocademy Visual Effects Awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:17.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The recipient, Morita Shinobu-san, criticized\Nthe director in his speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:21.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And the situation deteriorated to the point where\Nhe had to be pulled off the stage by bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This news is also all over\Nthe front pages of American newspapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch... why does my neck hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And the citizens are wondering if this was a challenge\Nby Japan directed at their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is amazing. The newspapers\Nand TV have his story all over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.13,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fscx80\c&H585F5C&\shad0\bord2.5\3c&HE9EEEE&\frz26.193\frx344\fry16\pos(257,205)}Japanese Wins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.13,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H646966&\shad0\3c&HA4A7A7&\frz23.044\frx354\fry10\pos(496,112)}And
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.13,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H666D6C&\fs34\an4\shad0\frz23.345\c&HE4E8E8&\frx348\fry6\pos(421,146)}Melees
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, TV stations might be rushing into our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy at the hospital last night... that was Morita-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he be in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, how did he get back to Japan so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff on TV last night was apparently pre-recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:48.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Morita-san rushed back\Nto submit his graduate thesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's the case, but who can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but isn't the deadline 5 P.M. today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:57.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, let's go to the hospital one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now eat a lot and get healthy, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here after all! Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?! Are you sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in the hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not blonde!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:14.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He overate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:19.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are YOU sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morita-san, you're all right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll go home for today, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hagu, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to take care of my precious Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, you brought back your payment in cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:44.57,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000\be1}Bag: {\3c&H635514&\be0}"majison" {\be1\3c&H000000&}(Madison Square Garden)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:39.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's close the bag... the wads of bills are popping out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He just overate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, on the honey-roasted in-flight snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they are pretty tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These are great! What the heck are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because the in-flight food is free...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was thinking I hadn't seen it in a while! So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru sent it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he asked me on the phone if there was anything I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:06.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:10.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and send it over! I don't have any change of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why my shirt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he broke into my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I need to go buy more honey-roasted peanuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What day is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Curried rice day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:21.77,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Many Japanese families have a day of the week when curried rice is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wasn't expecting anything out of you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:25.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:30.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been captured! Help me, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time. Let's go, Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:35.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Sensei is trying to save you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:41.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it really doesn't feel like it's been\Na year. He hasn't changed at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, he's gotten worse as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you actually make a graduate thesis in just four hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. But I think he just wants to take him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To the person who's been waiting for Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:58.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After I buy a book on historical material in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:03.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go look after the store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll go part of the way together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:21.21,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, actually, there's a book that I wanted as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.75,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:23.88,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.09,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.38,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.26,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, do you want to go get lunch together also?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.18,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What about looking after your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.72,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, my big brother is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Many words came to my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:44.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But they all seemed too unnatural and embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even bring them to my lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:55.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just absent-mindedly watched the brown hair that\NI like so much turn transparent in the winter sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:00.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your current job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:06.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's going okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just going to be the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hiring other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting more workers brings other problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:18.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think we'll just do what the two of us can do for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked that one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:28.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised by how much my heart stung\Nfrom Mayama saying, "The two of us."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:45.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I should... um... get going to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:57.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting frustrated for feeling so saddened by just those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:06.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't stop the mounting frustration at myself\Nfor venting that frustration on Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only twenty minutes left until the deadline\Nfor submitting your graduate thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:30.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that even you aren't capable of\Nfinishing this in twenty minutes, Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:31.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my graduate thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can finally turn it in to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept it, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mocademy Awards, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:07.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've certainly done it again. Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I won't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,CG? Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's getting so cocky these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how wonderful of an award it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:19.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as you're a student in the sculpture department...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:22.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept anything but a sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:30.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Out of the thousands of students that I've taught,\Nyou were number one or two in terms of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:33.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a rose blooming in a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:41.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Morita, although roses are beautiful,\Nit is truly difficult to maintain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:46.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They get infested with insects, plagued with infections, and hurt\Nboth themselves and those around them with their thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:52.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A lifeless rose can't outshine a healthy dandelion in its beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Gramps, you're so snooty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tickling me, telling me that I'm beautiful like a rose...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:04.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that a person with an enormous amount of talent\Nmust put in an equally enormous amount of effort lest he fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:10.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita, I have been in love from the bottom\Nof my heart with your talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:14.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last thing I can do for you as your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:18.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you, my precious student, about the reality of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:24.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept anything for your graduate thesis\Nother than a completed sculpture piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my farewell gift to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.59,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not listening to a word I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I won't accept anything but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:38.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:50.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Handmade... Moreover, the entire thing is made of pure gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:53.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Tange!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.45,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\shad0\fs35\fsp2\be1\bord0.8\fscy90\c&HF7FFFF&\pos(439,75)}Accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:13.38,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1950)\shad0\bord0.8\be1\fs44\c&HF7FFFB&\pos(293,157)}Morita Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:13.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1950)\shad0\bord0.8\be1\fs44\c&HF7FFFB&\pos(456,342)}will be graduating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:22.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that this year's graduate thesises have all been accepted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:26.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All the professors who have gathered here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For the future of all our students...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Professors! It's spilling, it's spilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary Cross Counter Toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, what a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:52.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, they finished it off German-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can graduate without any regrets now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't German-style like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:02.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1100,800)\bord1.5\fs39\be1\c&H7778AC&\an4\shad0\3c&HE8EFF5&\pos(114,71)}German-style {\c&HA1BEC0&}(Image)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(191,214)\fsp2}Prost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.34,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\shad0\bord0.5\be1\fs21\c&H4E689B&\3c&H92C2D6&\pos(317,158)}*They haven't even taken a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:16.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, Hanamoto-kun, we've finally been able\Nto make it to this day again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to have my students' graduate\Nthesises successfully accepted again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really takes the weight off your shoulders, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll be teaching another set of students again soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:26.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:32.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'm sure that Professor Tange can\Nreturn to a relaxing life as a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the light too bright, Gramps? You might want this over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morita! You can't put that over his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:41.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:03.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down, Morita. I can walk on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overexert yourself, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:19.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, you've gotten so light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've gone through a lot of hardship while I wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the one that made him lose weight...\NOver the course of eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:32.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We might say this and that, but Morita-san\Nreally likes Professor Tange, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:36.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita's affection is a double-edged sword, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:52.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You yelled at me and hit me a lot, but the\Npast eight years have been a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:58.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, don't talk so much. My head hurts. Just get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:17:05.26,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kousha no ura no hosoi michi wa sono mama puuru ni tsuzuiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:17:05.26,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}The narrow path behind the school led to the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hanamoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:18.69,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}natsu no mizu no iro to tomo ni kimi no kioku mo toonoite iku
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:18.69,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs24}Along with the summer color of the water, my memories of you are fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a teacher really isn't that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:13.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you care for a student,\Nthey all eventually graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:17.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they graduate, who knows how many\Nyears pass until you see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:20.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If things don't go right, you might never see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:29.91,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}ano higaerimichi de kimi to musunda yakusoku wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:29.91,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Even today, I still haven't been able to fulfill
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:29.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if teachers are like those school\Nghosts who can't even graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, Hanamoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:38.37,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}ima mo soshite kore kara mo hatasenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:38.37,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}That promise I made with you on the way home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.79,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}itsuka nakushite shimau yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.79,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}At this rate, I'll forget it someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure say some nasty things, Professor Tange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:51.26,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kimi wa wasurenain darou yurusenai yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:51.26,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}But you won't forget, right? It's unforgivable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take Gramps home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:58.27,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}dakara nando mo furikaetta
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:58.27,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}So I kept looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:55.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your payload will suddenly gain weight like Konaki-jijii\Nonce you pass the one kilometer mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't watch out, you'll see hell tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What payload? Am I Konaki-jijii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you idiot-idiot-idiot-idiot-idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:06.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, your underwear is showing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard, Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get tired, use a taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:22.75,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kudaranai koto de muki ni natte yubikiri de waratta kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:22.75,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Getting upset over stupid things, you smiled as we pinky swore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:19.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, another one of our precious senpais headed off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:23.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gracefully wiping up the numerous memories\Nand sorrows for the parting with a V-sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:35.31,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}chiisana kaban ni tsumeta mono wa kekkyoku boku no yume bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:35.31,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Though, in the end, only my dreams were stuffed into that small bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:32.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to join the Cinema Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:47.48,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}natsu no mizu no naka kara toutou kimi wa agaru koto wa naku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:47.48,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}In the end, you never came out of that summer water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how about you? Would you be\Ninterested in the Cinema Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:45.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. We're seniors, so we're busy\Nwith our graduate thesis and job hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's our senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:55.58,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}dare mo inai puuru de boku wa matteru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:55.58,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Alone by the pool, I wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:52.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm looking forward to the next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:19:00.16,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kimi to yakusoku shita kara
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:19:00.16,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Because I promised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:05.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, don't worry. I won't let you two be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:08.63,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}ie ni kaerou to suru to shibuki ga agari
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:08.63,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}When I try to go home, there's a splash...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, the ceramics room underwent a revamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:14.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. There's an art festival in Yokohama next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:15.47,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}boku wa sono ashi wo tomerunda
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:15.47,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}And it stops me in my tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And while we're there, do you all want\Nto go to the Chinatown there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:28.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking... that things haven't really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:37.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. Why would you dislike change at your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:44.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that you get shocked if things take a sudden turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's also refreshing, if you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:51.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:08.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Mo-Mo-Morita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:13.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Morita Shinobu.\NI just entered the Japanese Arts department this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:16.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to be precise, I transferred in as a third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a third year already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:23.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally learned after jumping out into the wide world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:24.87,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Kanji on the heads: {\be1\3c&H000000&}"stone"{\3c&H635514&\be0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:27.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That I still haven't studied enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.25,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even after you were here for eight years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, it's nice to make your acquaintance, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I look forward to learning from you, Professor Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:42.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me lots and lots over the next two years...\N{\fs24}More like four times that amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be under your tutelage for that amount of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:48.65,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He just whispered something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:51.98,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, he's actually all for staying\Nhere as long as possible once again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry—!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.13,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry—!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:15.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:28.06,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}waratta kao ni tsukekomare
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:28.06,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Taken advantage of by his smiling face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:31.23,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kuchi ni shita sake ni aorarete, oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:31.23,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Stimulated by the alcohol she drank
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:34.19,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sora misereta toki ururunda face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:34.19,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The tear that wells up when she's shown otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:37.90,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}ki ga sukkari sono ki ni natteru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:37.90,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}She'd already become all for it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:44.66,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:44.66,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.37,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.37,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:50.58,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}yume da to omoikonde mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:50.58,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Even if she tries to pretend that it was a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:56.38,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}monogataru kare no paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:56.38,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}His paper tells a different story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:22:01.97,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}shiroku samete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:22:01.97,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Becoming white and discolored
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:07.35,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}kumo no ue nobori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:07.35,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Ascending above the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:13.65,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,gin iro natsu tsunda yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:13.65,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The silvery summer's night she was picked up on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:28.25,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}shimetsukerareru mistake kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:28.25,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}She's being constricted by a mistake that won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:33.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: The time that was standing still begins to move.
